<p><span class="anchor" id="p52"></span>الثُّلُث عَلَيْهِمَا<a href="#p52" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p53"></span>بِالْقيمَةِ وَفِي قَول يقدم الْعتْق<a href="#p53" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
